{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-09e_106", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Trois Sonnets imitant trois autres de Pétrarque] *"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", quartier de juillet 1678 (tome III), p. 106-112."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les trois Sonnets qui suivent sont une imitation de trois autres de Petrarque, dont les premiers Vers vous sont marquez. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": "  Chaluet Avocat à Marseille en est l’Autheur. Il a beaucoup de talent pour-la Poësie, & doit donner au Public avant qu’il soit peu, la Traduction de ce qui nous reste des œuvres de Petrarque."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Imitation du Sonnet de Petrarque, qui commence, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Asprocuore e selvagio, e cruda voglia, &c"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "D'Un visage si beau la trompeuse douceur"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Cache aux yeux d’un Amant une ame si farouche !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si de quelque pitié ma peine ne la touche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mes dépoüilles, Iris, vous feront peu d’honneur."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Car enfin je succombe à ma vive douleur ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "soit que l’Astre du jour ou se leve, ou se couche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans cesse je languis la plainte dans la bouche."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Les larmes dans les yeux, & l’ennuy dans le cœur."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais quand il me souvient qu’une goute impuissante"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Peu caver les Rochers par sa chute fréquente,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Alors de quelque espoir mon esprit est flaté."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le cœur d’Iris est dur ; mais le long cours des larmes"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut amolir enfin toute sa dureté ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’est rien qui ne-cede à de si douces armes."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Imitation du Sonnet de Petrarque, qui commence, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Amor che vedi ogni pensiero aperto, &c."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet Libre."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "TOy qui n’ignores pas le secret de mon ame,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ny le rude chemin par où tu me conduis ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Amour, jette les yeux où tu portes ta flâme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Voy le fond de mon cœur que tu remplis d’ennuis."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Si je cesse d’aimer, je doy cesser de vivre :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais helas ! Que l’on souffre à courir apres toy !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu sçais que je n’ay pas des aisles pour te suivre ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne veux-tu pas avoir quelque pitié de moy ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah ! Ne me presse plus ; de loin je la voy luire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Cette douce lumiere où tu veux me conduire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour me faire trouver un glorieux trepas."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Laisse mon triste cœur, & souffre qu’il desire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Je me croy trop heureux, si lors que je soûpire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Celle pour qui je meurs ne s’en offence pas."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Imitation du Sonnet de Petrarque, qui commence, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "S'amor non è, ch'è dunque quel ch'i sento"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[2]", "text": " ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet Libre."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SI ce n’est pas amour, qu’est-ce donc que je sens ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais si c’estoit amour, Dieux ! Quelle est sa nature ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si c’est un mal, d’où vient ce qui flate mes sens ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Si c’est un bien, d’où vient la peine que j’endure ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pourquoy verser des pleurs, & pousser des soûpirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Si le feu dont je brûle a pour moy tant de Charmes ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et s’il est si contraire à mes libres desirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Dequoy peuvent servir les soûpirs & les larmes ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Poison délicieux ! Agreable tourment !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "As-tu tant de pouvoir sur le cœur d’un Amant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand mesme il ne veut pas consentir à sa peine ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Et si mon triste cœur de mille maux atteint,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Y consent en secret lors mesme qu’il s’en plaint,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Que je le trouve injuste, & que sa plainte est vaine."}]}]}]}]}